<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - The Limelight</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        /* Top bar */
        .top-bar {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 5px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #34495e;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 150px;
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo img {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #ecf0f1;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #3498db;
        }

        /* About Us Content */
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 3em;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 3em;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: -20px;
            top: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #3498db, transparent);
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            border-bottom: none;
            padding-bottom: 0.5em;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        }

        .section p, .section ul {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #34495e;
        }

        .section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .section ul li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section ul li::before {
            content: "â€¢";
            color: #3498db;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: -5px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }

        .footer-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .footer-section {
            flex: 1;
            margin-right: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .footer-section h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-form input,
        .contact-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
            background-color: #34495e;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .contact-form button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-form button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }

        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            nav ul {
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }

            nav ul li {
                margin: 0 10px;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 2em;
            }

            .section::before {
                left: -10px;
            }

            .footer-section {
                flex: 100%;
                margin-right: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .content {
                padding: 1.5em;
            }

            .section h2 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   
    
    <%- include('layouts/header.ejs') %>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <section class="section">
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>The Limelight aspires to be the premier web magazine in English, dedicated to showcasing original, incisive, and open-minded perspectives on philosophy, culture, arts, and religion. We aim to create a platform where innovative ideas can flourish and engage readers in meaningful discourse.</p>
            </section>
            <section class="section">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is twofold: to curate thought-provoking content that challenges conventional wisdom and to provide a stage for emerging talented writers. We strive to present a diverse array of literary works, including captivating stories, evocative poems, controversial articles, and engaging travelogues.</p>
            </section>
            <section class="section">
                <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Commitment to originality and innovation in thought</li>
                    <li>Platform for both established and emerging voices</li>
                    <li>Interdisciplinary approach to culture and ideas</li>
                    <li>Fostering open dialogue and intellectual curiosity</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            <section class="section">
                <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
                <p>Whether you're a reader seeking to expand your horizons or a writer looking to share your unique perspective, The Limelight welcomes you. Together, let's explore the depths of human creativity and intellect, shining a light on ideas that truly matter.</p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('layouts/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>